query:
INSERT INTO transactions (userId, accountId, categoryId, type, description, amount, currencyCode, direction, date)
SELECT 1, a.id, c.id, 'income', 'Monthly Salary', 500000, 'USD', 'credit', '2025-11-01'
FROM accounts a, categories c
WHERE a.userId = 1 AND a.type = 'bank' AND c.userId = 1 AND c.name = 'Salary'
LIMIT 1;
